For Tomahawk 2 and 3, you need a cross-compiler for Xtensa. M3 uses buildroot for that.
Just clone the repository to some location (this folder in this example):
$ git clone git://git.buildroot.net/buildroot

Now checkout the 2015.02 branch
$ cd buildroot
$ git checkout -b m3 2015.02

Finally, copy the config file and build it:
$ cp ../config-buildroot-iss .config
$ make -j

